Section 8
	Lecture 50: Bootstrap Data

1. Create New Package in the ej.springframework package: ej.springframework.bootstrap
2. Create new class named SpringJPABootstrap.java in the ej.springframework.bootstrap package
3. Implements ej.springframework.bootstrap.SpringJPABootstrap.java
 - Declare spring component using the spring @Component annotation
 - Declare private ProductService field
 - Declare Setter based DI for the ProductServcie using the @Autowired spring annotation
 - implements onApplicationEvent(..) method

4. Run and See the result behaviors